Package: cglm
Type: Package
Title: Compositional generalized linear models
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-08-30
Author: David Firth and Fiona Sammut
Maintainer: David Firth <d.firth@warwick.ac.uk>
Description: This package provides facilities for specifying and fitting the "Generalized Wedderburn" logit-linear model for a compositional response, and also (when the response vectors are free of zeros) the Aitchison-style multivariate linear regression based on logratio transformation of the response.  
License: GPL 2.0 or later.
